METEOR SWARM

Useage      : cast 'meteor swarm' <target>
Accumulative: No.
Duration    : Instantaneous.
Save	    : vs. spells for half damage.

Te only offensive spell more powerful then this is restricted to the most
dedicated of practicioners (disintigrate).  Meteor swarm will meet your
every expectation and is more then sufficient for most needs.  It does
level d10 damage per successful cast.

See Also: ENERGY DRAIN, DISINTIGRATE
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
